EASTERN NORTH ATLANTIC.
SCOTLAND-WEST COAST.
HAZARDOUS OPERATIONS.
1. HAZARDOUS OPERATIONS 1200Z TO 1900Z DAILY
   13 THRU 16 JUL WITHIN 27 MILES OF:
   A. 57-06.6N 008-22.2W.
   B. 57-34.9N 009-09.6W.
   VESSELS INTENDING TO ENTER AREA SHOULD CONTACT
   HEBRIDES RANGE CONTROL ON VHF CH 16 FOR ADVICE.
2. CANCEL THIS MSG 162000Z JUL.
